_sText:
This map is my first finished map, ever. 
I hope you like it.


This map is a modified version of my favorite map, cs_castleball.. Sorry for the ideatheft, but atleast I'm admitting it.. I love the original map so much, but only wished it was a bit different. with no textures. 

I made this map for my own fun, and I love playing it.. Works ok with bots, but they know where you are almost all the time.. 
So, better against humans than bots.. Sorry about that..
